<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.5.6">
<l>ēṭi laṅku tāmaraipōl cevvāy muṟuval ceytaruḷi</l>
<l>māṭu vanteṉ maṉampukuntu niṉṟār niṉṟā vūrpōlum</l>
<l>nīṭu māṭat taṉiccūlam pōḻak koṇṭal tuḷitūva</l>
<l>vāṭa laravat tārppōvā vaṇiyār vīti yaḻuntūrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The city where stands the one who stays, having entered my mind,</l>
<l>Coming near, graciously granting a smile with rosy lips like a lotus</l>
<l rend="indent">where petals gleam,</l>
<l>It seems is Aḻuntūr with beautiful streets where the sound of dance bells</l>
<l rend="indent">never ends,</l>
<l>As raindrops beat down from clouds, when split open by the single spire</l>
<l rend="indent">of the tall, raised shrine.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
